   <blockquote>
    <hr color="#000000" size="1"/>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
     The sign for "relationship" 
	can also mean "cooperation."
    </p>
    <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1" width="50%"/>
    <p>
     To show a relationship between two people, things, or ideas you can use a 
	back-and-forth sliding movement between the two items. This sign can also be 
	used to mean "cooperate."
    </p>
    <p>
     RELATIONSHIP / COOPERATION:
     <br/>
     <img border="0" height="217" src="/images/relati11.jpg" width="233"/>
    </p>
