     <img border="0" height="217" src="/images/relati10.jpg" width="233"/>
     <img border="0" height="218" src="/images/connectto4.jpg" width="221"/>
    </p>
    <hr color="#000000" size="1"/>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
     <br/>
     You can also use the general sign "CONNECT" to indicate that two things are 
	related or connected to each other. That they have a "bond."
     <br/>
     <br/>
